00:45:41.720 --> 00:45:43.020
&gt;&gt; Joe Sacco: Early 90s.

00:45:43.020 --> 00:45:44.320
&gt;&gt; Gary Groth: Yeah.

00:45:44.320 --> 00:45:45.620
