day with Charles Schultz.

00:48:09.040 --> 00:48:10.960
And we had a great time.

00:48:10.960 --> 00:48:12.530
We did an interview in his studio.

00:48:12.530 --> 00:48:15.460 position:56%
Then we walked over to his ice rink
where we hung out for another couple

00:48:15.460 --> 00:48:17.190
