00:48:17.190 --> 00:48:22.150
And at that time, just casually,
and I think spontaneously,

00:48:22.150 --> 00:48:27.160
I approached the subject of
collecting all the peanuts

00:48:27.160 --> 00:48:31.620 position:56%
