00:48:40.170 --> 00:48:42.570
They were scattered
all over the place.

00:48:42.570 --> 00:48:45.320 position:56%
They were poorly edited as a design.

00:48:45.320 --> 00:48:47.330
And I said, you know, it'd be great

00:48:47.330 --> 00:48:50.880
to have systematic collection
all uniformly designed of all

00:48:50.880 --> 00:48:52.180
of your work, all of Peanuts.

00:48:52.180 --> 00:48:55.930
And he said, "Well, I don't think
anybody'd be interested in that."

00:48:55.930 --> 00:48:57.230
And said, "No, no.

00:48:57.230 --> 00:48:59.220 position:56%
People would be interested in that."

00:48:59.220 --> 00:49:05.430
And then later on, I spoke to him
